      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that acting is key but for the initial casting calls we need to be more specific with the archetypes so we don't waste time. like, if we're looking for that specific \"street\" energy in a big city, what demographic or racial backgrounds usually fit that visual trope best? just trying to see what the industry standard expectation is for that kind of role.",
